# Modelo 3D: Octaedro (Cristal / Diamante)
# 6 Vértices, 8 Faces Triangulares

# --- Vértices (v x y z) ---
# Topo e Fundo
v  0.0  1.0  0.0
v  0.0 -1.0  0.0

# Pontos centrais (Plano X-Z)
v  1.0  0.0  0.0
v  0.0  0.0  1.0
v -1.0  0.0  0.0
v  0.0  0.0 -1.0

# --- Faces (f v1 v2 v3) ---
# Metade Superior (ligando o topo aos pontos centrais)
f 1 4 3
f 1 5 4
f 1 6 5
f 1 3 6

# Metade Inferior (ligando o fundo aos pontos centrais)
f 2 3 4
f 2 4 5
f 2 5 6
f 2 6 3
